### Application API Tests
### RestClient Extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

### ========================================
### 0. LOGIN (DO THIS FIRST!)
### ========================================
### Login to get JWT token for other requests
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "activeRole": "Donor"
}

### Copy the token from response above and paste in Cookie below ↓

### ========================================
### 1. SUBMIT APPLICATION (POST)
### ========================================
### Only Donor can submit
### Replace TOKEN_HERE with your token from login above
POST http://localhost:3000/api/application
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImQyODcxYjQ1LTUwNmItNGZmMy1hY2I4LTVmZjFhZDJjNGU5MSIsImVtYWlsIjoidGVzdEBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRG9ub3IiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUwNzM3NTEsImV4cCI6MTc3NTA3NzM1MX0.9lsz_vXhbNYZFzs3QxIxAmVqUHvrVlKX9lpF2l0kCPM

{
  "phone": "03001234567",
  "work_email": "creator@work.com",
  "address": "123 Main Street, Karachi, Pakistan",
  "facebook_url": "https://facebook.com/username",
  "instagram_url": "https://instagram.com/username",
  "linkedin_url": "https://linkedin.com/in/username"
}

### ========================================
### 2. GET MY APPLICATIONS (GET)
### ========================================
### See all your submitted applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/application/my
Cookie: token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImQyODcxYjQ1LTUwNmItNGZmMy1hY2I4LTVmZjFhZDJjNGU5MSIsImVtYWlsIjoidGVzdEBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRG9ub3IiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUwNzM3NTEsImV4cCI6MTc3NTA3NzM1MX0.9lsz_vXhbNYZFzs3QxIxAmVqUHvrVlKX9lpF2l0kCPM

### ========================================
### 3. GET ALL APPLICATIONS (GET)
### ========================================
### Admin only - See all applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/application/all
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 4. APPROVE APPLICATION (POST)
### ========================================
### Admin approves an application
### Replace APP_ID with actual UUID from database
POST http://localhost:3000/api/application/APP_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "Approved"
}

### ========================================
### 5. REJECT APPLICATION (POST)
### ========================================
### Admin rejects an application
POST http://localhost:3000/api/application/APP_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "Rejected"
}

### ========================================
### HOW TO USE:
### ========================================
### 1. Click "Send Request" above LOGIN first
### 2. Copy token from response
### 3. Replace TOKEN_HERE in other requests with your token
### 4. Replace ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE with admin user token
### 5. Replace APP_ID with real application UUID
### 6. Click "Send Request" on each test
